data.title: Funeral Prince Alexander of Belgium
data.meta_description: Queen Fabiola, Grand Duke Henri of Luxembourg, King Albert and Queen Paola of Belgium attend the funeral of Prince Alexander of Belgium in the Onze-Lieve-Vrouw church in Laken, Brussels, 4 december 2009. Prince Alexander of Belgium died at 29 november at the age of 67. Alexander is the half-brother of King Albert of Belgium and was married with Princess Lea. Photo: Patrick van Katwijk
